Phrase: The Mist Monster, confronted at the top of the mountain of the Senbon Torii, was formerly the lord of this mountain and was trying to counter the evil power of someone else, and it seemed to have been cursed in the thick Mist for a long time.
The Lord of the Mountain hid the children summoned by evil forces inside a torii labyrinth, and even took away all their diseases by his blessings, and has went to sleep again.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Perhaps that monster too, took the role of the Guardians of the Giant Trees.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Suppress the power of the Phantom Mist and save humanity. If that is the role of a guardian, then it has fulfilled it well.

Name: Putra
Phrase: I feel awful with all the battles in Iris Metro so far, like the one against Anna.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Let's not talk like that. There is no such thing as a good fight.

Name: Putra
Phrase: That's true. I said something weird. I'm feeling a little bit sorry for them.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: It's natural that you feel bad. We haven't defeated the true culprit of this incident.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: It doesn't end here. The really bad guys are behind that black torii.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Come to think of it, that fox girl said something like that too.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: It seems we can't continue the investigation like this. We have to go back and get ourselves back in shape.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I agree. We need to reorganise the troops and plan our strategy better. Let's take people who know about sorceries and dolls.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Of course, Miyako will help us again, right? You can't say you don't want to.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Over here is Hinayashiki...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: The Gate is open now. I can stop goshujin-sama's rampage...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Wait, Miyako? What are you doing?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'm sorry. I'm leaving here for now.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: W-W-Wha-What are you talking about? Did you hear what I just said!?

Name: Putra
Phrase: Exactly! You can't just recklessly fly off into the middle of nowhere! You don't know what's waiting for you.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Don't worry about that. Beyond this torii gate is Hinayashiki. It's an old mansion famous as a doll dumping site.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: That's...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, it's where I spent my childhood. It's my home.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Then we should plan together, especially if you know the area. It's easier to conquer a place if we know how to do it.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Then I'm sure we should do that, if we could. But this Gate will close soon. If that happens, it will be difficult to get into Hinayashiki.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Right now, people can't get near there because of the thick Phantom Mist and the sorcery. Even the Allied Forces are unable to deal with it, and this place has been declared a high-level danger zone. We cannot even go to the nearest garrison without permission.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Then let's all go through the torii gate right now. Let's all go in together and beat up the culprit.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: We can't do that.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Why not? Why can't we do that? Yoshino thinks that's not reasonable.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: After we defeated the monster, the Gate deteriorated. Look closer, Yoshino-chan, you'll see it.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: The Gate is under a strong spell to keep intruders out. Neither I nor Yoshino-chan can break it.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: ...But I am fine.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...Again?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: 'I am fine', you always say that. Miyako is always saying that, it's not fair. Why can't you rely on Yoshino?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Because Yoshino-chan is not good enough.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: You only think that.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: No, I'm not. I don't say random things. I say this because I really think you're not good.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I wish I could have told you more about the Hinayashiki. If you don't know anything about it, you might think about going there.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'm sorry. I wished I could have worded this better.
Miyako gently shook off Yoshino's hand that's been holding the sleeve of her kimono, and she started walking towards the black torii gate.
Beyond the Gate, where evil thoughts swirl, an eerie mansion can be seen. The mansion was covered in thick Mist, and countless Nishikese dolls were placed there.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Conductor-san, please keep Yoshino-chan away from the torii gate.
Are you sure you want to go alone?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes. That is what is needed to solve the problem. Even if we all go together, no one but me will be able to reach Hinayashiki.
Let me confirm one thing - Can you come back, Miyako?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I don't know.
...I understand.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yoshino-chan, don't look at me like that. I'll do my best to come back too.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Do you promise?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I promise. I will do my best to come back.
Miyako does not say that she will definitely come back. Yoshino firmly accepted what she meant. The two have just met and are asked to make a hard decision.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Ask Versailles about the rest of the story. She is the one who knows me best.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako, good luck...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Come back safely.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Come, Yoshino. Let's go. This is not over yet.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: That's right. Let's find someone who knows about sorcery and get them to open this Gate somehow.

Name: Putra
Phrase: I'm sure we can. So let's get away from here for now.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Mmm...
Fellow members of the Special Steel Squad walked up to Yoshino as her shoulders droop. The next battle is coming, so let's get off this mountain and back to the train as soon as possible.
They called out to each other and tried to leave the black torii gate, but...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Huh?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: What's wrong, Yoshino?'

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Body, can't move...

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Don't be silly, come on, grab my hand.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Can't. Can't move hands or legs.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Queensway, Putra, help us. We're going to carry Yoshino and pull her away from here.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Got it. Miss Putra, let's do this, okay? Ready!
It took several people to lift Yoshino's body. For some reason, Yoshino's body would not move from the front of the torii.
--And then the situation only got worse.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The Gate of the torii is out of control...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Oh no! Yoshino is being sucked towards the torii gate!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Yoshino's being dragged in! We have to stop it somehow!
The black torii gate released an even more sinister force than before, becoming a gigantic vortex that is about to suck Yoshino in.
The other Train Knights struggled to stop it, but the torii seems to be continue on and they couldn't stop it. It is clear that torii's target is Yoshino alone.
What can be seen beyond the torii gate is not Hinayashiki but... Hell.
Everyone present realised this - If she is sent there, she will never come back.
Vindictive vortex, kidnap emptiness. Curse One. One single grudge, cut off the ties of enmity.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: This power is...
Curse Two. Respect others and consume emptiness.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Body can move...

Name: Queensway
Phrase: The torii Gate is closing too! Miss Yoshino, run over here quickly!

Just as all hope was about to be lost, a Nishikese incantation was heard from out of nowhere. The power of the curse is so great that it surpasses the magical power of the Gate. With this, Yoshino succeeded in getting out of her predicament.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Someone closed the Gate with sorcery.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Not only that. The out of control torii gate was quelled in a single stroke.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Who in the world...?
I'm not familiar with Nishikese sorcery, but there's only a few people I know who can handle this advanced level of art.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Oh jeez, y'all are always up to no good. I haven't used sorcery this potent in a long time.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yuuzen...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Long time no see. Little sorceress-san. A rare blunder for ya, eh?
The woman who saved Yoshino was Yuuzen. She is a Nishikese sorceress and a former ally who fought alongside Ricardo and Mary. She was a member of the Resistance.
Yoshino kneeled to the ground as soon as she saw Yuuzen's face.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...Yuuzen, please. Please save Miyako...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Watch it. I cannot make that promise.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: However... I'll have to hear about her tale.
If I were to talk about someone who knows about sorcery and dolls, then look no further than her. We were enemies at one time, but that can't be said to be the case now. Yuuzen saved our lives twice.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Thrice to be precise, son of Ricardo.
Things took a surprising turn. Can we, the Special Steel Squad, save Miyako...?
